'''Highpoint''' was an area of [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] that contained the offices of [[The Taris Holofeed: Prime Edition|''The Taris Holofeed'']]. It was captured and destroyed by [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorians]] during the [[Taris Siege|invasion of Taris]].

